channel.title: Kelron|Original Project Insanity
channel.description:
[center][URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/10/unled1zd.png/][IMG]http://img10.imageshack.us/img10/6390/unled1zd.png[/img][/URL]
Kelron is based off the original Project Insanity that Sanity released. I don't intend to make this another re-make, but I would like to get more familiar with the Project Insanity networking as well as progress in the actual server. I would like to stabilize it more, cleaner and even further, package and network it myself. What I'd like to create out of this is a very fun pking server, with good combat and fun features.
[size=18pt][b]Progress[/b][/size]
[size=10pt][b]Client work[/b][/size]
Idx > Dat files 602 animations Pre-loading models 641 models Ep interface Used the [b]if (((Entity) (obj)).hitArray[j1] > 0) {[/b] method to disable the drawing so there's no 0. Fixed Lunar Interface - no more thread 5 Added and fixed Ancient Curse Interface - no more int problems Added fading hit marks - few unpacking errors (95) but I fixed them, as well as adding obv.
[size=10pt][b]Server work[/b][/size]
Insight into combat Improved magic formula Improved range formula Deleted the skilling-base for now Basic Ep System Pvp drops
